51都担心踏空  等节后他们冲进来的时候狠狠的摁一波<br/>如果他们明天回来了  直接送给他们，让他们套整个51连休息都闭不上眼睛<br/><br/>反正目前有先手，就等这些钱来不来就行了[s:ac:计划通]<br/><br/><br/>这些机构实在太恶毒了  我呸", "lou": 2321, "content_length": 325, "reply_to": 866353912, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777442714}, {"pid": 866354562, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:07", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天手上4个板了  其中2个20CM[s:ac:哭笑]<br/>趁我心情好你们可以问点不是个股的事 不然等我心情不好的时候只能拿你们出气了", "lou": 2322, "content_length": 96, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777442836}, {"pid": 866354836, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866354685,45974302,4519]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=4428686]浅浅浅丿[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:08):[/b]<br/><br/>那么大胆问问铁盒这个位置能持股过节吗[/quote]<br/>你就不要看他  按我之前说的做就行了  早点打工挣够本金把ETF换成688个股", "lou": 2323, "content_length": 69, "reply_to": 866354685, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777442968}, {"pid": 866355188, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 11, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866354888,45974302,4519]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42565054]路过的王小萌[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:09):[/b]<br/><br/>可以问板块吗狼大[s:ac:哭笑]请教一下有色板块和黄金期货的短中期[/quote]<br/>今天是被稀土带起来的  黄金主要是因为短期期货不会起来  为什么呢 因为鲍威尔是最后一次议息会议  接下去大家搞不清楚沃什那边是不是放水 所以这里不敢大动作<br/>所以除了铝我觉得短期可能是个小买点  其他都是震荡区间 说不上好和不好 反正不是主流", "lou": 2324, "content_length": 221, "reply_to": 866354888, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777443132}, {"pid": 866355414, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866355148,45974302,4520]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67141495]嘉然今天亏好多[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:11):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，今天开盘判断可以做正T，是基于出金日博弈和以前说过的做T方法结合判断的吗，还是说有什么咱们不了解的消息[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>对 就是基础判断 你们自己领悟吧 我怕说出来了 你们会自己抽自己几巴掌", "lou": 2325, "content_length": 67, "reply_to": 866355148, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777443234}, {"pid": 866356393, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 20, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:21", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866356093,45974302,4521]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60131057]yc419[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:19):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 游戏普涨 但是完美还在跌，是不是可以上了？今天外服上线，老外是不是爱玩这种gta+二次元味浓的[s:ac:羡慕][/quote]<br/>我做的是个股  我不玩一环 我觉得完美挣钱能力不行  一环这个挣不了钱。", "lou": 2326, "content_length": 67, "reply_to": 866356093, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777443686}, {"pid": 866356903, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 45, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866356125,45974302,4522]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=2454615]地狱看门猪[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:19):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大心情好分享一下接下来值得做的板块吧，最近轮动太快有点乱了[s:ac:瞎][s:ac:瞎][/quote]<br/>科技  科技  还是TM的科技<br/>无论做什么别的边缘的  一切的基础都是科技<br/><br/>AI大基建  上中下和附属。 半导体不也是AI大基建里面的。<br/>只是你看你喜欢做什么细分而已", "lou": 2327, "content_length": 141, "reply_to": 866356125, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777443920}, {"pid": 866357085, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 43, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866356778,45974302,4523]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67165063]熊猫射手[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:24):[/b]<br/><br/>有没有大佬说一下今天出金日早盘卖出错在哪，周一预判周三出金日会跌所以买入等拉高，周二就吃了绿柱子，所以今天开盘就卖了等着跌到差不多接回来，结果节奏完全踏错[s:ac:瞎][/quote]<br/>错在没有看我早盘第一句话 特地赶在25分之前发出来", "lou": 2328, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 866356778, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777443990}, {"pid": 866357145, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866356770,45974302,4523]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67154591]消缺二号机[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:24):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，想问问对算力租赁板块的看法，今天让减仓是因为资金不去顶红警协创反而去买不正宗的票，代表资金出现分歧了是吗？那明天利通分歧是不是反而是买点？[s:ac:喘][s:ac:喘][/quote]<br/>我不想说那边 我感觉危险系数开始加大", "lou": 2329, "content_length": 39, "reply_to": 866356770, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777444018}, {"pid": 866357456, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 7, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:29", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866357288,45974302,4524]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62084214]uml777[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:28):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，还想问下电池这种这么强的应该怎么做？之前通道上沿减了就再也补不回来了。后面给机会又怕补在半山腰。现在是完全目送了。没见过这么强的……[/quote]<br/>我分享过怎么卖加速的票了", "lou": 2330, "content_length": 29, "reply_to": 866357288, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777444162}, {"pid": 866357637, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 12, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866357261,45974302,4524]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61014703]嘟嘟嘟丶嘟[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:27):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，如果算计租赁要走调整，资金会不会向流向AIDC[/quote]<br/>倒也切不了这么快 估计会反复 反复的时候一般低位会更惨", "lou": 2331, "content_length": 55, "reply_to": 866357261, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777444240}, {"pid": 866358746, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 23, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:38", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866358272,45974302,4526]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42162697]包子music[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:35):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，借着心情好，可以问问南向这个月胜率高是为啥吗<br/><br/>标红的本月三次单日南向+100e以上的次日，上证指数均有+0.8%的涨幅(有一天收了上影十字星但收了+0.5%)<br/>今天是本月第四天，南向本月胜率百分百<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202604/29/jmQ2x-4smK21T3cSir-oc.jpg[/img][/quote]<br/>我也很奇怪  居然比我胜率高<br/>但是从他们第二次我就发现了 所以才和你们说", "lou": 2332, "content_length": 69, "reply_to": 866358272, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777444722}, {"pid": 866358898, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 14, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:39", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866358470,45974302,4526]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67165063]熊猫射手[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:36):[/b]<br/><br/>这倒是确实，我22分挂的单撤不了啦[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>你25分不能买回来么", "lou": 2333, "content_length": 23, "reply_to": 866358470, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777444789}, {"pid": 866359013, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 15, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866358411,45974302,4526]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1026163]john1chen[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:36):[/b]<br/><br/>最核心的力通跟老邪呢，这两只我都有，感觉老邪比较稳，反复的时候不会太狠吧[/quote]<br/>协创经常小作文 反正把握每一次小作文的机会进场都是对的 其他时间都不是进场时间。", "lou": 2334, "content_length": 81, "reply_to": 866358411, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777444836}, {"pid": 866359181, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 70, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:41", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866358923,45974302,4527]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143809]Rzzz二号机[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:39):[/b]<br/><br/>图哥的装逼技术不如你十分之一，真的不开玩笑[s:a2:lucky][/quote]<br/>那你不废话<br/>整个市场有多少个敢公域明牌告诉你了以后市场马上验证的？我这个胜率你以为市场很多?<br/>我TM已经快10了啊", "lou": 2335, "content_length": 110, "reply_to": 866358923, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777444911}, {"pid": 866359259, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866359084,45974302,4527]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67045282]颜控正义日记[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:41):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大今天收盘多少仓位啊[/quote]<br/>83%", "lou": 2336, "content_length": 8, "reply_to": 866359084, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777444940}, {"pid": 866359438, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866359323,45974302,4528]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38140916]huohuo277[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:42):[/b]<br/><br/>协创的基本面居然这么优秀？[/quote]<br/>他真有卡啊  他只是渠道不对而已  但是他真有卡啊", "lou": 2337, "content_length": 47, "reply_to": 866359323, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777445020}, {"pid": 866359924, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 70, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们这么多人这时候都看不出早上为什么能买么<br/>哪怕你们找理由都找不到么。。。<br/>晚上我得空在和你们说吧  说完估计你们会自己扇自己巴掌  [del]确实看过但忘记的那种感觉[/del][s:ac:嘲笑]", "lou": 2338, "content_length": 151, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777445242}, {"pid": 866360166, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 14:49", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866359859,45974302,4528]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61055412]recomditeness[/uid] (2026-04-29 14:46):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大对今年大宗商品粮食细分怎么看, 我觉得上半年化肥紧俏应该会波及到春耕以及粮食 逻辑是否可行[/quote]<br/>化肥国内的没事 老美那边也消化完了  部分玉米改了土豆<br/>化肥这个事更多影响工业用气<br/>影响最大的我估计是印度，不过他们有钱 应该会翻倍价格买化肥。", "lou": 2339, "content_length": 137, "reply_to": 866359859, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777445349}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155491, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109336, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "米璐璐6666LLL", "digest": 0,